{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_05",
  "title": "敵わぬ相手",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～～っ……。なんてことでしょう……\n私としたことが、みっともない振る舞いを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… What a situation…\nI've behaved so embarrassingly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 10.0355554581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "うまく歌えないことを他人のせいにして\n私は未熟者ですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Blaming others for not being able to sing well…\nI'm still inexperienced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "endTime": 17.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you're here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4333333333,
      "endTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、私を探しに？\nわざわざ、申し訳ございません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ were you looking for me?\nI'm sorry for the trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0333333333,
      "endTime": 26.2335599264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.312331136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "もう落ち着いたみたいね\nなら、戻ってレッスンの続きをしなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you've calmed down.\nIn that case‚ go back and continue your lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.312331136,
      "endTime": 31.520970567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.712331136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですわ、私、{user}さんに\n酷い態度を取ってしまいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's no use. I…\nI've been horrible to {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.712331136,
      "endTime": 39.185823090899994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3789978027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "合わせる顔がありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no face to meet him…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3789978027,
      "endTime": 42.2342358112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私、決して{user}さんのことが\n嫌いな訳ではないのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that I hate\n{user}-san or anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4456644694,
      "endTime": 47.9469798724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "こんな経験、初めてで、どう振る舞えばいいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my first time for this‚ so I don't know how to act…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1456644694,
      "endTime": 52.765233580300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "彼は貴方が思っているより、ずっと大人よ\n普通に今まで通りのすずでいいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He's much more mature than you think.\nJust be your usual self‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3456644694,
      "endTime": 60.0358007112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.2456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それより、これを読んでみなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But first‚ read this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2456644694,
      "endTime": 62.852421919499996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66666660000118
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.0456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "それはなんですの？　楽譜のようですけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is this? It looks like sheet music…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0456644694,
      "endTime": 67.362013785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.5456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "今回の曲について、彼なりに気が付いたことを\n昨日、書き込んだそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He wrote down his observations about this song.\nApparently‚ he stayed up all night doing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5456644694,
      "endTime": 72.7382950465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そのせいで、昨日は彼が徹夜だったみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of that‚ he must have been tired yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9456644694,
      "endTime": 76.47373711270001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "これは……歌の特性や歌い方のコツ……\n私の歌い方の癖まで……こんなに細かくびっしり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This… It's about the characteristics of the song and how to sing it…\nEven my singing habits are written down in such detail…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7456644694,
      "endTime": 88.8455282847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.0456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……\n私が気が付かなかったことも沢山あります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's amazing…\nThere are so many things I didn't notice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0456644694,
      "endTime": 94.2763676325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4789978027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈のそばで一番、彼女の歌を聴いていた彼にしか\n出来ないことね。すずに伝えたかったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only someone listened to Mana's song the most can do this.\nHe wants to let you know‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4789978027,
      "endTime": 102.5898140907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "彼女の歌の良さを、すずに、多くの人に知ってほしい\n彼にとっても、とても大切なのよ、麻奈の曲は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He wants Suzu and more people to know about Mana's wonderful singing.\nFor him‚ Mana's songs are very important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7789978027,
      "endTime": 112.4789978027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.7789978027
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.912331136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "（私は麻奈様の曲を完璧に理解したつもりでいました）\n（けど、このメモを見たら、全然だって分かりますわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I thought I understood Mana-sama's songs perfectly…)\n(But looking at these notes‚ I realize I knew nothing…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.912331136,
      "endTime": 122.7215357059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.112331136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "（{user}さんの必死さが伝わってくる……）\n（本当に、麻奈様のことを……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "({user}-san's desperation comes through…)\n(Truly‚ about Mana-sama…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.112331136,
      "endTime": 130.2496781667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4456644694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "胸が苦しくなってきましたわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's making my heart ache…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4456644694,
      "endTime": 133.30500685369998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.512331136,
      "endTime": 135.3451202471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
